<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="record-n">record <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'rekɔːd/    美 /'rekərd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>记录；记载；履历：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a personal record 
个人履历</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Keep a record of</strong> what interests you most. 
记下你最感兴趣的事。</p><footer>人教④ – 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(尤指体育运动的) 纪录：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>set a</strong> new world <strong>record</strong> in the 200-meter dash.
她创造了200米短跑的新世界纪录。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in record time</strong>
用最短的时间</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>唱片：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make a record
录制唱片</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="break-beat-cut-the-a-record">break / beat / cut the / a record</h3>
<p>1.<strong>打破纪录：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’s hoping to break the record for the 100 metres.
她希望能打破百米纪录。</p></div></div>